text: İzmir Atatürk Anadolu Teknik Lisesi (İzmir Atatürk Anatolian Technical High School), established in 1993, as a part of İzmir Atatürk Andolu Teknik, Teknik ve Endüstri Meslek Lisesi (İzmir Atatürk Anatolian Technical, Technical and Industrial Profession High School), and is one of the oldest Anatolian Technical High Schools of İzmir and Turkey. The high school selects its students with the standardized test of National Anatolian Technical High Schools Examination. It is one of the leading schools in Turkey performing a total success at the National University Entrance Examination. The current manager is Sedat Başlar. ==References== *İzmir Atatürk Anadolu Teknik Lisesi website Category:Educational institutions established in 1993 Category:High schools in İzmir Category:1993 establishments in Turkey
